-- Sanofi-Aventis Denies It Offered Genzyme a Price Range at Sept. 20 Meeting
-- B y   A l b e r t i n a   T o r s o l i
-- 2010-10-08T07:48:27Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-08/sanofi-aventis-denies-it-offered-genzyme-a-price-range-at-sept-20-meeting.html
Sanofi-Aventis SA denied that it
offered Genzyme Corp. a price range in a Sept. 20 meeting
between the chief executives of the companies.  “We offered no price range,” Sanofi spokesman Jean-Marc
Podvin said by telephone.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
